WEBVTT

00:49.424 --> 00:52.302
EPISODE 13

01:21.331 --> 01:22.332
Hey.

01:23.500 --> 01:24.542
Where are you going?

01:25.502 --> 01:26.753
I'm going home.

01:33.301 --> 01:34.511
Can you see me?

01:41.476 --> 01:42.727
The thing is...

01:43.603 --> 01:44.687
Just come here.

01:46.231 --> 01:47.148
Jun-hui.

01:48.608 --> 01:49.609
Just come here.

01:50.110 --> 01:51.528
Don't be like that.

01:53.279 --> 01:54.697
Didn't you hear me?

02:10.922 --> 02:12.173
Long time no see.

02:13.133 --> 02:14.259
How have you--

02:20.098 --> 02:22.600
- Let's go.
- What are you doing?

02:23.184 --> 02:24.477
Your dad is here.

02:25.103 --> 02:26.187
Don't mind him.

02:28.148 --> 02:29.482
You shouldn't treat him like this.

02:30.233 --> 02:32.402
I know how you must be feeling, but--

02:32.527 --> 02:33.528
You know?

02:35.113 --> 02:36.739
And still, you're being like this?

02:37.615 --> 02:38.908
Are you sure you know how I feel?

02:39.492 --> 02:40.535
What do you know?

02:41.035 --> 02:42.412
How much do you think you know?

02:45.790 --> 02:48.042
Fine, I don't know. I don't know anything.

02:48.459 --> 02:50.962
I did what I thought I should do,
and I won't change my mind.

02:51.379 --> 02:53.798
I agreed to meet him today,

02:54.048 --> 02:55.341
so don't make a fuss about it.

02:56.342 --> 02:57.385
Jin-a.

02:57.969 --> 02:59.637
Don't act like a kid.

03:02.473 --> 03:04.934
He's not some stranger. He's your dad.

03:06.853 --> 03:07.937
Says who?

03:09.522 --> 03:11.774
Who the hell said that man is my father?

03:14.402 --> 03:15.445
Jun-hui.

03:16.279 --> 03:17.363
Do as you please.

03:17.780 --> 03:19.157
You can do whatever you want,

03:21.117 --> 03:22.702
but don't expect me to do the same.

03:45.099 --> 03:46.142
I'm sorry about that.

03:46.851 --> 03:48.102
It's okay.

03:50.104 --> 03:52.315
So, are we canceling the plan?

04:08.039 --> 04:09.123
Damn it!

04:44.325 --> 04:47.453
It wouldn't be a bad idea
to have dessert first.

04:48.288 --> 04:49.247
Okay.

04:56.587 --> 04:57.588
After you.

05:22.488 --> 05:23.406
Where are you going?

05:24.741 --> 05:26.159
Jun-hui, where are you going?

05:31.414 --> 05:34.125
I suspected
that something might be going on

05:35.460 --> 05:36.419
between you and Jun-hui.

05:40.965 --> 05:43.509
Every time you talked about him
at the hotel...

05:44.677 --> 05:45.845
How should I put it?

05:46.721 --> 05:48.431
Shall I say that you seemed nervous?

05:51.059 --> 05:53.436
Anyway, I could tell
that something was up.

05:55.146 --> 05:56.272
I'm sorry.

05:56.355 --> 05:58.066
That too.

05:58.816 --> 06:01.944
I wondered why you kept saying sorry,
but it must have been about him.

06:03.863 --> 06:04.822
I'm sorry...

06:08.743 --> 06:10.453
It makes me happy.

06:12.580 --> 06:16.042
I mean, it's you, Jin-a. I'm happy to know

06:16.876 --> 06:18.669
that you are going out with Jun-hui.

06:20.797 --> 06:21.714
I think it's wonderful.

06:24.675 --> 06:25.968
Do you really mean it?

06:27.887 --> 06:31.015
You know, I've been told
that I'm too honest with women.

06:35.061 --> 06:37.021
Thank you for being so understanding.

06:37.105 --> 06:39.315
Why wouldn't I be?

06:40.566 --> 06:41.692
Do your parents know?

06:45.363 --> 06:46.280
Yes.

06:48.699 --> 06:50.076
They must be happy for you, right?

06:53.871 --> 06:56.582
Well, they didn't see it coming,

06:56.666 --> 06:58.501
so I think they are a bit taken aback.

07:00.294 --> 07:01.754
I see.

07:02.839 --> 07:04.882
But they will come to understand
of us soon.

07:04.966 --> 07:06.801
You know my parents.

07:07.218 --> 07:09.345
They may be conservative,

07:09.554 --> 07:12.682
but they are not that unreasonable.

07:13.182 --> 07:15.685
If so, why did they make you
go on a blind date?

07:25.903 --> 07:26.863
Well...

07:30.408 --> 07:32.994
This really hurts my pride.

08:12.783 --> 08:13.826
Go on.

08:33.304 --> 08:35.473
Sir, could you turn the radio off?

08:35.556 --> 08:36.974
Sure.

09:36.826 --> 09:37.868
Hello.

09:41.872 --> 09:43.124
Are you trying to reach Jun-hui?

09:43.207 --> 09:44.500
Is he up there?

09:44.834 --> 09:45.876
No, he isn't.

09:46.627 --> 09:48.713
- He's not at work?
- No, he got off work.

09:49.088 --> 09:51.507
I am not completely sure
if he got off work,

09:51.591 --> 09:54.260
but he took his bag and left.
He seemed to be in a rush.

09:54.385 --> 09:55.386
When?

09:56.137 --> 09:58.848
I don't know. What time was it?

09:59.599 --> 10:00.975
Maybe around 7:00 p.m.?

10:03.686 --> 10:05.146
- Thank you.
- Sure.

10:15.489 --> 10:17.575
Something just came up.

10:19.744 --> 10:21.746
I'm going back this week.

10:23.873 --> 10:25.124
I'm not hiding anything.

10:26.125 --> 10:28.377
I don't keep secrets from you.

10:29.045 --> 10:31.047
It's not a big deal, that's why.

10:32.798 --> 10:33.674
Yes.

10:35.051 --> 10:37.553
There will be tickets
since it's not peak season.

10:39.513 --> 10:41.766
Don't worry.
Don't forget to lock the doors at night.

10:43.059 --> 10:44.769
I'll call you before I get on the plane.

10:50.232 --> 10:51.233
Okay.

11:24.850 --> 11:25.810
Hello.

11:33.192 --> 11:34.652
Have this as your late-night snack.

11:35.319 --> 11:37.321
- Goodness, thank you so much.
- I got it for you.

11:37.696 --> 11:39.865
By the way, your brother was very drunk.

11:40.116 --> 11:42.201
- He came home?
- Just a little while ago.

11:42.952 --> 11:44.745
He was completely wasted.

11:45.204 --> 11:46.705
I've never seen him like that.

11:46.956 --> 11:48.082
Thank you.

11:52.628 --> 11:56.090
Hey, Seo Jun-hui! Hey!

11:56.966 --> 11:59.093
How much did you drink?

11:59.176 --> 12:01.679
Come on. Get up!

12:01.971 --> 12:04.265
If you're going to sleep,
sleep in your bed.

12:04.348 --> 12:07.601
Gosh, what's gotten into you?
How much did you drink?

12:09.311 --> 12:11.147
Sleep in your bed. Lie down.

12:17.903 --> 12:19.196
My gosh.

12:29.039 --> 12:30.666
My goodness.

12:31.500 --> 12:34.086
What have you been up to?

12:39.049 --> 12:40.718
Hey, let go!

12:40.885 --> 12:42.470
You crazy punk. Stay still.

12:44.930 --> 12:47.099
What on earth have you been up to?

15:02.318 --> 15:04.695
Did he really break up with Jin-a?

15:13.454 --> 15:14.663
You startled me.

15:14.914 --> 15:16.498
These are the stores you're in charge of.

15:19.710 --> 15:22.296
Why don't you keep managing
the Suseo store?

15:22.379 --> 15:23.964
Are you teasing me or what?

15:25.007 --> 15:26.842
There's no point anymore.

15:27.801 --> 15:29.178
Why would you take it like that?

15:29.261 --> 15:30.346
Why wouldn't I?

15:32.056 --> 15:35.851
Things got a bit awkward
between you and Ms. Seo, right?

15:36.769 --> 15:38.395
Why would you ask me that all of a sudden?

15:39.063 --> 15:41.440
Well, I just figured
that things cannot be the same

15:41.523 --> 15:43.567
since you two are not just friends anymore

15:43.651 --> 15:45.069
now that you are dating her brother.

15:45.361 --> 15:47.029
It's not like that.

15:47.196 --> 15:48.489
I only suggested that

15:48.572 --> 15:50.449
because you've been managing
the store until now.

15:51.116 --> 15:54.203
Well, it's not like I am eager
to keep managing the store.

15:54.995 --> 15:57.289
But if it's uncomfortable for you to--

15:57.373 --> 15:58.958
I'll take it over. Give it to me.

16:01.418 --> 16:03.712
Since when were you so supportive of her?

16:07.257 --> 16:08.384
Is something wrong?

16:09.134 --> 16:10.219
Later.

16:16.016 --> 16:16.976
Gosh.

16:25.901 --> 16:26.986
Hello.

16:27.152 --> 16:30.072
Seung-cheol, it's Jin-a.

16:31.156 --> 16:32.282
Yes, hi.

16:34.368 --> 16:35.411
He's not there?

16:36.578 --> 16:38.372
Are you saying he didn't come to work?

16:38.872 --> 16:42.167
Yes, I was told that he took the day off.

16:45.045 --> 16:46.213
For what reason?

16:46.505 --> 16:48.298
I'm not sure.

16:48.632 --> 16:50.759
Hasn't he called you?

18:49.545 --> 18:50.629
Hello?

18:51.505 --> 18:52.631
Sang-gi?

18:53.632 --> 18:54.883
May I ask who this is?

18:55.425 --> 18:56.760
I'm Gyeong-seon's dad.

18:58.720 --> 18:59.555
Oh, my.

19:00.097 --> 19:03.225
It's been so long.

19:04.017 --> 19:06.061
Your number hasn't changed.

19:06.562 --> 19:09.481
No, it hasn't. I didn't expect
to get a call from you.

19:09.565 --> 19:10.524
How have you been?

19:11.358 --> 19:12.609
I'm doing well.

19:13.735 --> 19:15.445
Oh, I see.

19:16.446 --> 19:18.824
May I ask what the occasion is?

19:19.575 --> 19:20.576
Are you busy?

19:21.952 --> 19:24.454
Of course not. I'm retired now.

19:24.788 --> 19:27.166
I'm just spending every day
not doing much.

19:27.749 --> 19:29.418
Then why don't we meet today?

19:31.170 --> 19:32.129
Pardon?

19:38.594 --> 19:40.888
It's only been a few days
since I bought groceries.

19:40.971 --> 19:42.556
Why are we out of so many things already?

19:44.141 --> 19:47.644
Maybe I should stop making kimchi
starting from this year.

19:47.895 --> 19:49.897
The kids don't even eat at home anyway.

19:50.606 --> 19:52.274
What about Gyeong-seon and Jun-hui?

19:53.734 --> 19:55.319
I'm not their mom.

19:55.986 --> 19:56.987
Don't be like that.

19:57.404 --> 19:59.114
You shouldn't take it out on them.

19:59.198 --> 20:00.782
Are you going to cut ties with them?

20:01.700 --> 20:02.784
I will if I have to.

20:03.327 --> 20:04.161
My gosh.

20:05.245 --> 20:06.997
I'm trying my best right now.

20:07.164 --> 20:10.500
You and Seung-ho
keep telling me that I'm wrong.

20:10.584 --> 20:12.169
So I'm trying hard to hold myself back.

20:12.252 --> 20:13.420
What more do I need to do?

20:13.503 --> 20:15.505
- What did I do?
- You nagged me.

20:23.096 --> 20:24.097
What now?

20:25.515 --> 20:26.516
Well...

20:27.768 --> 20:28.810
Never mind.

20:29.061 --> 20:30.020
What is wrong with you?

20:32.105 --> 20:33.106
Well, the thing is...

20:35.234 --> 20:37.444
Gyeong-seon's dad wants to see me today.

20:38.445 --> 20:39.863
He must be in Korea.

20:40.781 --> 20:41.615
Why would he...

20:42.282 --> 20:43.408
Why does he want to meet?

20:43.909 --> 20:45.077
I don't know.

20:45.160 --> 20:47.329
Tell him to forget it. Don't meet him.

20:47.829 --> 20:49.414
I already said I would.

20:49.498 --> 20:50.916
My gosh, Yoon Sang-gi!

20:51.667 --> 20:54.628
Are you trying to ruin
your daughter's life?

20:56.255 --> 20:57.714
I'm a dad.

20:58.924 --> 21:00.759
I'm Jin-a's father!

21:04.304 --> 21:05.681
Just what do you take me for?

21:06.556 --> 21:07.933
Stop disrespecting me!

21:09.268 --> 21:10.310
How dare you!

21:24.533 --> 21:26.618
What do you mean they were persuaded?

21:27.452 --> 21:28.495
Kong Cheol-gu...

21:29.246 --> 21:32.124
Mr. Kong has been taking some
of the female employees out for meals

21:32.207 --> 21:33.917
and telling them not to tell on him.

21:34.001 --> 21:35.836
He even said
that they are at fault to a degree,

21:36.670 --> 21:39.214
and it would be good for everyone
to just call it even.

21:39.756 --> 21:40.757
So?

21:41.508 --> 21:42.759
They're young,

21:43.218 --> 21:44.469
and he's their boss.

21:44.553 --> 21:46.513
I think they are pressured
to keep quiet about it.

21:47.180 --> 21:48.140
Well...

21:48.557 --> 21:49.599
I think

21:50.517 --> 21:52.227
they feel relieved in a way.

21:53.228 --> 21:54.229
What do you mean?

21:55.856 --> 21:57.607
Jin-a can't be the only victim.

21:58.608 --> 21:59.651
But most of them are scared

21:59.735 --> 22:01.445
that they might have to come forward
as well.

22:03.363 --> 22:06.533
It seems like they are going to use him
as an excuse to stay quiet.

22:08.368 --> 22:10.370
They are trying to make Jin-a
fight the battle alone.

22:14.082 --> 22:16.168
What if Jin-a changes her mind as well?

22:24.676 --> 22:25.969
You wanted to see me?

22:27.846 --> 22:30.057
- Are you busy these days?
- No, not really.

22:30.515 --> 22:32.768
But of course, I'm working very hard.

22:33.602 --> 22:34.603
You should be.

22:35.062 --> 22:36.313
But it doesn't seem you are.

22:37.814 --> 22:40.984
I don't understand what you mean.
Please be more specific.

22:42.027 --> 22:43.111
Sure.

22:43.695 --> 22:44.696
That's not a problem.

23:02.380 --> 23:03.256
This is...

23:03.465 --> 23:04.466
Move your hand.

23:07.677 --> 23:09.262
What you just did was sexual harassment.

23:10.514 --> 23:11.848
No, wait. That was...

23:15.435 --> 23:17.104
If you try to cover this up,

23:17.187 --> 23:19.981
I can make you pay
for something you didn't even do.

23:22.234 --> 23:23.819
- Would you like me to do that?
- No, ma'am.

23:25.862 --> 23:27.948
I'd better not see you lurking around

23:28.323 --> 23:29.658
our female employees.

23:52.806 --> 23:54.266
Is Jin-a at her desk?

23:56.768 --> 23:57.769
Okay.

24:20.584 --> 24:22.377
I'd like two Americanos.

24:22.460 --> 24:24.045
- For here, please.
- Okay.

24:44.816 --> 24:47.569
Is there something going on with Jun-hui?

24:49.779 --> 24:51.031
I can't reach him.

24:51.281 --> 24:52.490
He didn't even go to work.

24:53.909 --> 24:54.951
He didn't go to work?

24:56.328 --> 24:57.537
I guess you didn't know.

24:57.746 --> 24:59.080
He took the day off.

25:00.624 --> 25:02.292
I thought you two broke up.

25:04.544 --> 25:05.837
Then what's wrong with him?

25:05.921 --> 25:08.506
Why did he get drunk to the point
where he has to skip work?

25:08.673 --> 25:10.091
Did he drink a lot?

25:10.717 --> 25:13.053
He wasn't just drunk.
He was completely wasted.

25:13.803 --> 25:14.888
He even hurt his hand.

25:14.971 --> 25:17.515
Maybe he got into a fight
or broke something.

25:17.599 --> 25:19.059
He got hurt?

25:19.142 --> 25:20.352
It wasn't serious.

25:21.978 --> 25:24.648
Did nothing happen between you two?

25:30.654 --> 25:33.406
I met your dad.

25:35.158 --> 25:37.160
He came to meet me at the office.

25:37.869 --> 25:39.871
Jun-hui happened to see me with your dad.

25:42.916 --> 25:45.877
What's wrong with you?
Why would you meet our dad?

25:45.961 --> 25:48.213
So that you can ask him
to help you get married to Jun-hui?

25:49.172 --> 25:51.424
I know I make a lot of mistakes,

25:51.675 --> 25:53.009
but I'm not that thoughtless.

25:56.721 --> 25:58.556
He got you guys gifts,

25:59.724 --> 26:01.434
but he couldn't give them to you himself.

26:03.520 --> 26:04.854
I was worried

26:05.563 --> 26:08.400
that I might end up making things worse
between you and your dad.

26:08.483 --> 26:10.360
It's not like I didn't think it through.

26:11.027 --> 26:11.861
So...

26:12.737 --> 26:14.281
how did Jun-hui react?

26:14.906 --> 26:16.157
Did he fight with Dad?

26:17.492 --> 26:18.952
He didn't even look at him.

26:19.744 --> 26:22.372
Plus, he probably hated the fact
that I met up with your dad.

26:23.039 --> 26:24.291
He was really angry.

26:25.417 --> 26:27.585
I've never seen him that angry before.

26:28.086 --> 26:29.254
That's all that happened.

26:30.046 --> 26:31.965
And I haven't been able to reach him
since then.

26:35.760 --> 26:39.097
He's probably not home now, right?

26:39.931 --> 26:41.099
He's not there.

26:41.182 --> 26:43.893
I made hangover soup for him
and went over, but he wasn't there,

26:43.977 --> 26:45.562
so I thought he had left early for work.

26:46.813 --> 26:48.315
Where on earth did he go?

26:52.485 --> 26:53.403
I think...

26:54.529 --> 26:56.281
I made a mistake.

26:58.575 --> 27:01.036
He got so worked up in front of your dad,

27:02.078 --> 27:04.414
so I told him to stop acting like a kid.

27:08.918 --> 27:10.670
It must have hurt his feelings.

27:11.921 --> 27:14.341
Everyone is driving me nuts.

27:15.175 --> 27:16.468
My gosh.

27:58.551 --> 28:00.387
HERE LIES JEONG IN-HYE

28:13.650 --> 28:14.692
Mom.

28:16.611 --> 28:17.654
It's been a while, right?

29:09.914 --> 29:10.957
I'm sorry I am late.

29:11.040 --> 29:12.751
I'll make it up to you.

29:21.468 --> 29:23.762
I wish he'd try not to worry me.

29:41.696 --> 29:42.864
You're still here.

29:43.740 --> 29:45.909
Do you know how many years
I've been commuting by subway?

29:45.992 --> 29:47.619
I can go home with my eyes closed.

29:49.078 --> 29:51.664
Take my phone.
I'll call you from my work phone.

29:52.665 --> 29:54.167
Seriously...

29:54.959 --> 29:56.586
That way, I won't worry.

30:52.267 --> 30:54.143
Like I've explained to you,

30:54.310 --> 30:57.647
Jin-a might say a lot of things about--

30:59.482 --> 31:00.358
Well...

31:00.817 --> 31:03.444
there are many people who are
at the same job level as you, right?

31:04.863 --> 31:06.656
There are many assistant managers indeed.

31:08.491 --> 31:10.910
Everyone must be fiercely competing
for a promotion.

31:11.786 --> 31:14.414
Well... Who's the ace?

31:14.873 --> 31:16.207
The one who stands out.

31:17.458 --> 31:18.626
I'm not sure.

31:19.210 --> 31:22.255
I guess higher-ups
would have a better idea about that.

31:22.839 --> 31:24.007
Then it'd be Jin-a, of course.

31:26.217 --> 31:28.970
Obviously, I'm rooting for you,

31:29.053 --> 31:32.015
but it's...
You know how things are done here.

31:32.098 --> 31:34.142
The ones
who suck up to higher-ups would...

31:34.475 --> 31:35.894
Well, you know.

31:37.103 --> 31:38.646
But I don't think like that.

31:38.980 --> 31:40.356
Of course not.

31:46.112 --> 31:48.364
Obstacles should be removed
sooner than later.

31:48.448 --> 31:49.824
Considering many aspects...

31:50.742 --> 31:51.659
Wouldn't that be wise?

31:54.329 --> 31:55.997
I think you're right, sir.

31:56.080 --> 31:58.416
Of course, I'm right. In my whole life,

31:58.499 --> 31:59.334
I've never...

32:00.293 --> 32:01.169
Yes, nonsense.

32:01.544 --> 32:03.796
People who talk nonsense
are the ones that I hate the most.

32:24.150 --> 32:25.818
What do you want to talk to me about?

32:26.569 --> 32:28.446
You look so serious.

32:29.530 --> 32:31.032
No, it's nothing serious.

32:33.326 --> 32:34.827
What did you want to discuss?

32:35.244 --> 32:36.079
Go on.

32:38.539 --> 32:39.958
Well, it's just about...

32:41.000 --> 32:43.586
Back when you were
starting this company...

32:45.046 --> 32:48.299
You see, money is a funny thing.

32:49.968 --> 32:54.138
You helped me out a lot
when I started this company.

32:54.347 --> 32:56.182
I'm still very grateful for that.

32:57.517 --> 32:59.435
We're a family,
so you don't need to thank me.

33:00.019 --> 33:02.814
I know that our wives are distant cousins,

33:03.272 --> 33:05.608
but we're still a family, you know.

33:05.692 --> 33:07.986
My wife is also grateful
for all of your help.

33:08.069 --> 33:11.781
That's why we wanted to pay you back
at a high interest rate,

33:11.864 --> 33:14.283
but you refused
saying it makes you uncomfortable.

33:14.367 --> 33:16.202
Who charges a family member interest?

33:16.536 --> 33:18.329
Gosh, that'd be so petty.

33:22.417 --> 33:23.543
I must say,

33:24.377 --> 33:26.337
you keep emphasizing that we're a family.

33:32.051 --> 33:34.887
I'm like your older brother, you know.

33:35.221 --> 33:37.849
I mean, it's not like
we're complete strangers or something.

33:38.182 --> 33:39.225
Gosh.

33:43.146 --> 33:46.149
You should make sure to sort things out

33:46.566 --> 33:48.484
before the problem rises to the surface.

33:49.235 --> 33:50.153
You know,

33:50.737 --> 33:53.072
I draw a clear line
between work and my personal life.

33:54.365 --> 33:55.408
Of course.

33:56.034 --> 33:59.370
Everyone should draw a clear line
between work and personal matters.

34:05.376 --> 34:07.253
Will this be enough?
Should we order more food?

34:07.336 --> 34:09.380
- No, don't order more.
- This should be enough.

34:10.965 --> 34:12.383
By the way, what's gotten into you?

34:12.467 --> 34:14.135
Why are you treating us?

34:14.343 --> 34:16.345
It's so hard to find a time
that works for everyone.

34:16.679 --> 34:18.931
I've always wanted to treat you guys.

34:20.058 --> 34:22.310
I'm so glad that we don't have
company dinners these days.

34:22.477 --> 34:24.270
I wish we could hang out like this
more often.

34:24.353 --> 34:25.980
- Right?
- Yes, totally.

34:29.233 --> 34:32.195
By the way, do you guys know this?
About the sexual harassment issue...

34:32.987 --> 34:35.448
People could say
that it was partially our fault.

34:35.531 --> 34:37.075
Why? We're the victims.

34:38.076 --> 34:41.162
Some will definitely say that we probably
gave them a reason to behave like that.

34:41.829 --> 34:44.165
Are you saying people will think
that we asked for it?

34:44.248 --> 34:47.001
Gosh, don't get so worked up.

34:48.169 --> 34:49.545
I'm not talking about you guys.

34:53.257 --> 34:55.593
I feel bad for saying this, but...

34:57.637 --> 34:59.889
How should I put this? Jin-a was...

35:01.224 --> 35:02.308
way too much of a pushover.

35:04.769 --> 35:07.522
Well, don't get me wrong.

35:08.397 --> 35:11.025
She's very friendly, you know.

35:11.109 --> 35:14.362
That's why she crosses the line sometimes
without even realizing it.

35:16.114 --> 35:19.951
Why? Bo-ra and I used to
warn you about it.

35:20.743 --> 35:22.245
We told you not to learn that from her.

35:28.626 --> 35:32.046
It's true that we, the female employees,
are the victims,

35:33.005 --> 35:34.048
but people might say

35:34.132 --> 35:36.926
some of us are equally to blame
for what happened.

35:38.052 --> 35:39.720
I'm a bit concerned about that.

35:41.264 --> 35:42.223
Especially...

35:43.224 --> 35:46.352
the ones who are close to Jin-a

35:48.062 --> 35:50.439
are more likely to be unfairly blamed.

36:04.620 --> 36:05.663
Aren't you leaving?

36:06.414 --> 36:09.458
Oh, I will. I'm going to leave in a bit.

36:10.835 --> 36:12.170
You must have a lot on your mind.

36:13.713 --> 36:15.506
No, I'm fine.

36:16.090 --> 36:18.759
How can you be fine? I know
you're under more stress than anyone else.

36:20.553 --> 36:22.263
What exactly are you talking about?

36:22.346 --> 36:25.057
Well, I'm just saying I know
how stressful things must be for you.

36:25.141 --> 36:26.475
You're stressed out, aren't you?

36:29.478 --> 36:31.647
No, I'm not stressed out about anything.

36:32.773 --> 36:34.400
Everything's fine regarding work.

36:34.775 --> 36:36.819
But if you're talking about anything else,

36:37.028 --> 36:38.779
I must say you are being a bit nosy.

36:42.033 --> 36:43.367
I must have crossed the line.

36:44.493 --> 36:46.579
Don't get me wrong. See you.

36:56.214 --> 36:58.299
What's he doing?

37:03.137 --> 37:04.180
Hey, Seung-ho.

37:05.389 --> 37:06.682
Why do you sound so excited?

37:08.059 --> 37:09.435
Are you with Jun-hui?

37:11.520 --> 37:12.730
I was going to ask you that.

37:14.106 --> 37:15.233
Do you know where he is?

37:16.025 --> 37:17.109
Where are you?

37:18.653 --> 37:19.904
I'm at school.

37:20.529 --> 37:22.448
Why is Jun-hui's cell phone turned off?

37:23.574 --> 37:24.742
I don't know.

37:25.743 --> 37:26.994
Did you two fight?

37:27.370 --> 37:28.496
None of your business.

37:29.830 --> 37:30.831
I guess you did.

37:32.333 --> 37:33.918
Do you know where he might be?

37:34.168 --> 37:35.544
Or anyone he could've met?

37:37.880 --> 37:39.799
You're being overly obsessive.

37:40.716 --> 37:41.717
I'll hang up.

37:42.551 --> 37:45.638
Tell Jun-hui to call me
if you get a hold of him.

37:46.180 --> 37:47.265
Tell him yourself.

37:50.059 --> 37:51.352
What's her problem?

37:59.652 --> 38:00.695
Hey.

38:02.405 --> 38:03.531
My gosh.

38:04.407 --> 38:05.574
Goodness.

38:06.117 --> 38:07.451
- Take a seat.
- Okay.

38:07.702 --> 38:09.203
It's been so long.

38:10.079 --> 38:11.330
- Have you been doing well?
- Yes.

40:14.662 --> 40:15.746
Let me.

40:28.801 --> 40:30.219
What do you not like about Jun-hui?

40:31.929 --> 40:33.431
Why can't you approve of him?

40:34.473 --> 40:35.558
My goodness.

40:38.269 --> 40:40.062
No, it's not like that.

40:40.479 --> 40:41.355
Is it because of me?

40:42.773 --> 40:45.860
No, that's not...
What are you talking about?

40:47.361 --> 40:49.530
Then why are you
against their relationship?

40:49.613 --> 40:51.365
I'm not against it.

40:52.867 --> 40:57.580
They've been close friends
ever since they were kids.

40:57.955 --> 40:59.373
What a silly excuse.

41:00.791 --> 41:01.792
I know.

41:02.710 --> 41:06.046
To be frank, they have an age gap.

41:07.131 --> 41:08.674
That's even more ridiculous.

41:09.717 --> 41:11.677
Don't you have any better excuses?

41:15.347 --> 41:17.641
I feel frustrated as well.

41:21.729 --> 41:23.814
I shouldn't be your reason
to disapprove of Jun-hui.

41:24.857 --> 41:27.860
Are you worried that I might depend
on my children once I get old?

41:28.819 --> 41:30.571
Why would you think that?

41:30.654 --> 41:32.740
Then what is it?

41:34.492 --> 41:36.452
Give me one good reason

41:36.827 --> 41:39.955
why you stomp all over my kid's pride
and humiliate him.

41:46.462 --> 41:47.338
Gosh.

41:56.555 --> 41:58.766
Are you that angry at the fact

42:00.184 --> 42:02.019
that I met your dad?

42:03.229 --> 42:04.897
Do you really have to get angry like this?

42:06.982 --> 42:07.983
Why can't I?

42:09.485 --> 42:12.112
I've been thinking of him
as a stranger until now.

42:12.613 --> 42:14.365
But because of my girlfriend,

42:15.241 --> 42:17.034
I have to consider him my father.

42:18.035 --> 42:20.454
You went behind my back
and set things up yourself

42:21.580 --> 42:24.250
so that I'd have no choice
but to accept him.

42:25.292 --> 42:26.544
How can I be fine with that?

42:29.463 --> 42:30.923
It's not like I wasn't aware of that.

42:31.006 --> 42:32.132
Then

42:32.716 --> 42:34.343
you should've discussed with me first.

42:35.135 --> 42:36.845
You should've asked me first.

42:38.806 --> 42:40.766
You're going to say
you didn't want to worry me.

42:41.433 --> 42:43.561
You always use that as an excuse
to hide things from me.

42:47.773 --> 42:49.483
It's not like you've never lied to me.

42:50.317 --> 42:52.236
Didn't you lie to me as well?

42:52.736 --> 42:53.737
About what?

42:55.614 --> 42:58.492
About how your mom told me
to break up with you

42:58.659 --> 42:59.868
and slapped me across my face?

43:01.870 --> 43:03.247
That kind of stuff?

43:13.549 --> 43:14.758
Why didn't you tell me?

43:16.927 --> 43:17.970
Because I knew

43:18.971 --> 43:20.055
how you'd react.

43:22.433 --> 43:23.976
You'll cry and apologize to me.

43:24.977 --> 43:27.479
You won't believe me no matter
how many times I tell you I'm fine,

43:27.563 --> 43:29.189
and you'll try to put on a smile for me.

43:30.649 --> 43:31.692
Every time that happens,

43:33.736 --> 43:35.029
all I can do is to hold your hand

43:37.698 --> 43:39.867
and hug you.
Do you know how that makes me feel?

43:41.452 --> 43:42.536
It drives me crazy.

43:43.412 --> 43:44.872
It makes me feel so miserable.

43:47.750 --> 43:49.001
I don't know much about parents.

43:50.502 --> 43:51.795
They say, "Parents are like that.

43:52.713 --> 43:53.797
That's what parents do,"

43:55.382 --> 43:56.884
but I don't understand what that means.

43:59.511 --> 44:01.513
That's why I wasn't scared to date you.

44:03.515 --> 44:04.933
I was ready to endure anything

44:05.643 --> 44:07.311
as long as I have you by my side.

44:07.394 --> 44:08.228
But...

44:11.315 --> 44:12.816
this guy that I don't even understand

44:13.567 --> 44:14.902
nor I want to try to understand...

44:16.612 --> 44:18.697
Someone who I never want to see again
suddenly shows up

44:18.781 --> 44:19.948
and acts like his my dad.

44:21.700 --> 44:23.285
Even worse, in front of a woman I love.

44:25.454 --> 44:27.206
How can you expect me
to be okay with that?

44:29.625 --> 44:32.378
Am I supposed to feel grateful?

44:33.462 --> 44:34.880
Why? Why should I?

44:37.841 --> 44:40.052
- Still, he's your father.
- That mindset is also a problem.

44:41.428 --> 44:43.097
I'm not acting like a kid.

44:44.390 --> 44:45.641
You're making me seem like I am.

44:47.726 --> 44:51.146
You think I should be understanding of him
and cut him some slack.

44:51.814 --> 44:55.067
That mindset of yours makes me
seem like I'm being immature.

44:58.862 --> 45:00.239
So are you saying it's my fault?

45:02.032 --> 45:04.034
That's not my point.

45:05.119 --> 45:06.245
Then what's your point?

45:06.829 --> 45:08.789
You just said
that I'm making you feel that way.

45:09.998 --> 45:11.625
- Jin-a.
- You're saying

45:11.708 --> 45:12.793
I'm making you seem immature

45:12.876 --> 45:15.796
by acting all grown-up and generous.

45:17.005 --> 45:19.133
Fine, that's what I was doing.

45:19.633 --> 45:21.385
You're right. Are you happy now?

45:23.512 --> 45:24.930
- Jin-a.
- What?

45:26.807 --> 45:29.059
- Don't you get my point?
- Of course, I get it.

45:29.143 --> 45:31.895
You're telling me to stop acting
as if I'm more mature.

45:32.896 --> 45:35.399
You want me to stop acting
like I'm the grown-up.

45:35.482 --> 45:36.608
I get it.

45:45.951 --> 45:47.619
What? Am I wrong again?

45:48.412 --> 45:49.371
What is it then?

45:56.545 --> 45:57.629
Never mind.

45:58.505 --> 45:59.840
I'm sorry

46:00.048 --> 46:02.634
for being stubborn
when I don't even know anything.

47:11.537 --> 47:13.247
Can you open this for me?

47:13.997 --> 47:15.082
Thank you.

48:26.194 --> 48:27.195
Hey, Gyeong-seon.

48:32.075 --> 48:33.118
Okay.

49:18.080 --> 49:19.998
Gosh, we're here.

49:20.082 --> 49:22.334
- My gosh, what's going on?
- We're home.

49:22.959 --> 49:25.629
What's wrong with my wife?

49:25.712 --> 49:27.714
- Come on inside.
- I should go.

49:27.881 --> 49:30.634
It's okay. Come inside.

49:31.927 --> 49:34.179
My gosh, look at you.

49:35.180 --> 49:36.682
What was the word?

49:36.765 --> 49:40.018
Look at how you keep your shoes on
like an American.

49:40.102 --> 49:42.854
We're in Korea right now, okay?

49:43.230 --> 49:44.231
Okay.

49:46.400 --> 49:50.362
Welcome to our home. Come on in.

49:51.279 --> 49:54.449
Honey! Mi-yeon!

49:55.075 --> 49:56.451
Come this way.

49:56.702 --> 49:58.245
- Okay.
- Here.

49:59.079 --> 50:00.831
Sit right here.

50:03.166 --> 50:05.919
My wife's just really shy.

50:07.254 --> 50:08.922
Mi-yeon,

50:09.464 --> 50:11.216
what are you doing?

50:12.050 --> 50:14.302
Mi-yeon.

50:14.928 --> 50:17.139
What are you doing?

50:17.806 --> 50:19.766
Mi-yeon.

50:24.062 --> 50:25.480
Have you gone crazy?

50:26.523 --> 50:28.108
Yes, I have.

50:28.191 --> 50:30.652
- I'm crazy for love.
- That's enough.

50:30.736 --> 50:33.447
Why did you bring him home?
Have you lost your mind?

50:34.156 --> 50:36.908
Let's not be so selfish.

50:36.992 --> 50:37.868
What?

50:38.076 --> 50:41.371
Our kids will suffer
if we keep being too selfish.

50:41.455 --> 50:44.207
What are you saying?
Hurry up and send him home.

50:44.291 --> 50:45.792
Come on. Hurry up.

50:45.876 --> 50:47.919
You can't treat our guest like this.

50:48.003 --> 50:50.005
And he's my guest.

50:50.088 --> 50:52.507
Guest? I've had enough of this.

50:52.591 --> 50:54.092
Should I kick him out myself?

50:54.176 --> 50:55.802
- Get out of my way.
- Don't you dare.

50:56.219 --> 50:58.138
I'll kick you out instead.

51:01.933 --> 51:03.518
Don't you dare disrespect me.

51:07.522 --> 51:10.317
He must have completely lost his mind.

51:17.032 --> 51:18.950
Let's not drink anymore.

51:19.201 --> 51:21.036
Are you drunk already?

51:21.995 --> 51:25.248
I'm completely fine right now. My gosh.

51:33.840 --> 51:34.883
Hey.

51:35.967 --> 51:38.261
Today, I feel...

51:39.262 --> 51:40.430
really...

51:42.140 --> 51:44.059
How should I put this?

51:45.143 --> 51:47.354
I feel happy.

51:48.980 --> 51:51.441
But I also feel sad at the same time.

51:54.194 --> 51:55.403
Sentimental.

51:56.655 --> 51:59.866
That's how I feel right now.

52:02.911 --> 52:04.120
Do you understand

52:05.247 --> 52:08.500
how I feel right now?

52:10.418 --> 52:11.628
Yes, of course.

52:13.463 --> 52:16.091
We get along so well.

52:16.174 --> 52:18.885
- Here, let me pour you a glass.
- Sure.

52:19.177 --> 52:21.972
Here you go.

52:22.055 --> 52:24.015
- That's enough.
- Here you go.

52:25.058 --> 52:28.979
My gosh. Honey, what are you waiting for?

52:29.062 --> 52:31.106
Bring us some food.

52:31.189 --> 52:32.858
Don't do that.

52:34.401 --> 52:38.405
My wife does everything I ask her

52:39.072 --> 52:40.073
to do.

52:42.325 --> 52:44.369
Mi-yeon!

52:45.078 --> 52:47.330
Mi-yeon!

52:49.249 --> 52:50.250
See?

52:50.333 --> 52:53.461
She comes out as soon as I call her.

53:00.510 --> 53:01.553
My goodness,

53:02.888 --> 53:04.347
it's been a while.

53:04.931 --> 53:06.766
Yes, it has.

53:07.976 --> 53:10.437
I'm sorry for visiting so late at night.

53:10.520 --> 53:11.646
You should be.

53:13.106 --> 53:14.024
I'll be off soon.

53:14.107 --> 53:17.152
What are you talking about?

53:17.444 --> 53:20.238
He's going to stay over tonight.

53:22.908 --> 53:26.411
Why are you just standing there?
Bring us something to eat.

53:26.578 --> 53:27.746
Sit back down.

53:43.011 --> 53:45.138
Then should we start drinking?

53:45.221 --> 53:46.556
That sounds great.

53:47.307 --> 53:50.018
Here you go. Cheers.

53:55.941 --> 53:58.568
Let me pour you another one.

54:01.279 --> 54:02.447
My gosh.

54:12.207 --> 54:13.667
I heard you met Dad.

54:15.919 --> 54:17.504
Jin-a told me everything.

54:17.671 --> 54:19.381
Why didn't you go to work today?

54:22.217 --> 54:24.719
Where were you?

54:25.303 --> 54:26.304
I went to see Mom.

54:28.598 --> 54:31.309
What did she say? Was she proud of you?

54:34.479 --> 54:36.439
You must have felt really frustrated.

54:41.319 --> 54:43.363
I could always find an answer
after seeing Mom.

54:44.781 --> 54:46.741
But I couldn't do so today.

54:47.242 --> 54:49.327
Maybe Mom also felt frustrated.

54:50.787 --> 54:53.123
Do you think everything you do is right?

54:57.460 --> 54:58.962
What did I do wrong?

55:00.964 --> 55:04.217
Do you think I'm fond of Dad?
Do you think I love him?

55:04.676 --> 55:08.221
But what can we do?
He's still the only parent we have.

55:09.556 --> 55:10.682
Do we need him?

55:11.057 --> 55:12.434
It's not because we need him.

55:12.517 --> 55:16.021
We just deal with each other
since we live under the same sky.

55:16.521 --> 55:18.523
If you hadn't been so lenient with him,

55:18.606 --> 55:21.484
he wouldn't have dared to consider himself
my dad and meet Jin-a.

55:22.235 --> 55:24.404
You're so ignorant.

55:25.113 --> 55:27.574
I know Jin-a has a knack
for making mistakes,

55:27.657 --> 55:30.243
but she knows how to differentiate
right from wrong.

55:30.618 --> 55:32.495
He wanted to meet her
because he had no other way

55:32.579 --> 55:34.080
to give us the gifts he got for us.

56:04.486 --> 56:07.113
- You should take a seat.
- No, it's all right.

56:07.655 --> 56:09.908
He wants you to join us.

56:19.125 --> 56:20.335
I heard that you've been

56:21.336 --> 56:23.296
taking such good care of my kids.

56:24.798 --> 56:26.132
Not really.

56:26.424 --> 56:28.176
Gosh, what are you talking about?

56:29.219 --> 56:31.471
She took better care of them
than she took care of our own.

56:32.305 --> 56:35.183
She adores Gyeong-seon and Jun-hui.

56:40.313 --> 56:43.233
What do you hate so much
about Jin-a dating Jun-hui?

56:46.277 --> 56:47.695
I want to hear your reason.

56:50.615 --> 56:52.117
I'm really curious.

56:52.200 --> 56:55.078
Well, do I have to...

56:58.414 --> 56:59.457
It must be Jin-a.

57:08.716 --> 57:11.803
The best daughter in the world is here.

57:11.886 --> 57:13.596
Come join us.

57:13.680 --> 57:15.390
Hey, you should get changed first.

57:20.395 --> 57:22.272
Call Gyeong-seon or Jun-hui.

57:22.355 --> 57:24.357
Tell them to come and get him right now.
Hurry up.

57:24.441 --> 57:25.483
What is going on?

57:25.567 --> 57:27.485
You got us into this mess.
Why are you asking me?

57:27.694 --> 57:28.945
Call them right now.

57:29.612 --> 57:31.698
Gosh, why should I call them?

57:32.407 --> 57:33.450
Shall I call them myself?

57:33.992 --> 57:35.034
Mom.

57:35.285 --> 57:36.411
Would that be better?

57:37.287 --> 57:38.371
Please don't.

57:39.789 --> 57:42.167
You think you can ignore
everything I say now, don't you?

57:44.586 --> 57:46.796
All right, fine.
I'll take him back to his hotel.

57:46.880 --> 57:49.382
What is wrong with you?
Why would you do that for him?

57:49.466 --> 57:51.217
Do you take him
as your father-in-law or what?

57:51.634 --> 57:52.927
You're jumping the gun again.

57:53.553 --> 57:55.513
It's not like he's a stranger.

57:56.139 --> 57:58.558
He's my friend's dad.
Why can't I give him a ride?

57:59.309 --> 58:02.228
Don't make a fuss about everything.

58:02.520 --> 58:04.939
Is this my fault?
Was I the one who got us into this mess?

58:07.775 --> 58:08.776
Fine.

58:09.360 --> 58:11.738
It's my fault. It's all my fault.

58:12.363 --> 58:15.241
I'm at fault for all the problems
in the world. I'm the one to blame.

58:16.201 --> 58:17.452
What do you want me to do?

58:17.869 --> 58:21.247
Do you want me to disappear forever?
Would that make you happy?

58:21.372 --> 58:23.791
You brat. How can you say such a thing?

58:23.875 --> 58:25.376
How dare you try to threaten me?

58:25.585 --> 58:27.754
Gosh, stop spewing nonsense.

58:27.837 --> 58:29.881
Just call them already!

58:31.382 --> 58:32.425
Whatever.

58:33.426 --> 58:36.429
You can call them yourself
or kick him out. Do whatever you want.

58:36.513 --> 58:38.765
Gosh, seriously. Can't you just call them?

58:39.265 --> 58:40.433
You prick!

58:44.395 --> 58:45.688
What did you just say?

58:45.855 --> 58:50.151
You've done nothing to be proud of.
How can you be so brazen?

58:50.235 --> 58:51.945
- Dad, please.
- I can't stand this anymore.

58:52.529 --> 58:54.030
- Dad, why...
- Gosh.

58:54.197 --> 58:55.240
Gosh, Dad!

58:56.533 --> 58:58.159
- Dad.
- My gosh.

58:58.326 --> 59:00.119
How I live my life
is none of your business.

59:01.371 --> 59:02.413
And one more thing.

59:03.831 --> 59:04.666
I don't think

59:05.375 --> 59:07.418
your daughter is good enough for my son!

59:15.510 --> 59:18.429
What kind of person
gets married three times?

59:34.445 --> 59:35.572
I'm not going to drink.

59:38.074 --> 59:39.242
I'm going to go see Jin-a

59:40.118 --> 59:41.536
after I drop you off.

59:44.539 --> 59:46.249
I knew that she's good at keeping secrets,

59:46.874 --> 59:49.627
but I feel so bad now.

59:51.963 --> 59:54.549
I'm coming clean
because I've been feeling so guilty.

59:54.632 --> 59:56.259
I told her to end it with you.

59:58.428 --> 01:00:01.097
I got so angry when I found out
that she was going on a blind date.

01:00:02.724 --> 01:00:04.851
I did regret a little after saying that.

01:00:07.478 --> 01:00:10.523
Hey, wouldn't it be weird
if I wasn't bothered by it at all?

01:00:12.567 --> 01:00:13.693
I know that, but...

01:00:15.111 --> 01:00:16.613
I know how you must be feeling,

01:00:16.946 --> 01:00:18.740
but can you please try
not to hurt Jin-a...

01:00:20.783 --> 01:00:21.826
Gosh.

01:00:21.909 --> 01:00:24.412
You're totally crazy for her.

01:00:26.456 --> 01:00:28.499
Okay, fine. I won't say anything to her
from now on.

01:00:30.418 --> 01:00:32.211
If you're going to sit there
looking all upset,

01:00:32.295 --> 01:00:33.963
just go see that woman
you're so crazy for.

01:00:34.922 --> 01:00:37.634
I want to drink a little
before heading home.

01:00:38.301 --> 01:00:40.928
Well... Just drink at home, then.

01:00:41.596 --> 01:00:43.222
Do I have to keep
bending over backwards...

01:00:45.975 --> 01:00:47.977
MS. KIM

01:00:51.439 --> 01:00:52.440
Hello?

01:00:54.525 --> 01:00:55.360
Sorry?

01:00:56.027 --> 01:00:56.903
My dad is there?

01:01:27.141 --> 01:01:27.975
You came.

01:01:45.034 --> 01:01:46.327
I'm sorry.

01:01:47.870 --> 01:01:49.872
An apology isn't enough.

01:01:50.581 --> 01:01:51.499
Mom.

01:01:51.958 --> 01:01:54.627
Gyeong-seon,
you're Jun-hui's older sister.

01:01:54.711 --> 01:01:56.379
Aren't you worried about his future?

01:01:57.004 --> 01:01:58.673
I mean, you care about him so much.

01:01:58.756 --> 01:02:00.883
How can you not even try to stop him?

01:02:01.050 --> 01:02:02.593
Why do you bring that up now?

01:02:02.677 --> 01:02:05.513
Because I have to.
I can't let this drag on forever.

01:02:06.639 --> 01:02:07.932
And you, Jun-hui.

01:02:08.725 --> 01:02:10.393
Did you not hear a word I said?

01:02:11.102 --> 01:02:13.813
Are you that disrespectful
because you grew up without parents?

01:02:15.231 --> 01:02:17.233
What did you just say?

01:02:18.609 --> 01:02:19.569
Gyeong-seon.

01:02:19.652 --> 01:02:22.071
That's right. We grew up without parents.

01:02:22.739 --> 01:02:24.907
But no one has said that we're impolite

01:02:24.991 --> 01:02:27.160
or treated us like rude brats.

01:02:27.702 --> 01:02:29.078
Enough, okay?

01:02:29.996 --> 01:02:30.997
I'm sorry.

01:02:31.748 --> 01:02:33.249
If you're really sorry,

01:02:33.583 --> 01:02:36.085
you shouldn't have let this happen
from the get-go.

01:02:36.627 --> 01:02:39.046
It's already a disaster,
and it'll only get worse.

01:02:39.297 --> 01:02:40.298
Look at him.

01:02:40.798 --> 01:02:42.759
Can't you see how hopeless your father is?

01:02:43.092 --> 01:02:44.761
You two won't be any different.

01:02:44.844 --> 01:02:46.304
Mom, please.

01:02:46.387 --> 01:02:47.847
Keep your mouth shut!

01:02:48.598 --> 01:02:50.391
Can't you at least pretend
to listen to me?

01:02:50.683 --> 01:02:52.059
Aren't you old enough now?

01:02:52.143 --> 01:02:54.437
Why are you being so immature?

01:02:54.645 --> 01:02:56.814
This is about your future.

01:02:56.898 --> 01:02:59.025
You need to think about your future!

01:02:59.108 --> 01:03:00.359
Are you saying

01:03:00.443 --> 01:03:02.737
- Jun-hui would ruin her future?
- Whether he does or not,

01:03:02.987 --> 01:03:04.822
I can't approve of him no matter what.

01:03:06.157 --> 01:03:08.117
And we're not the only ones
who are against it.

01:03:09.577 --> 01:03:12.038
Your dad also said
that he can't approve of Jin-a.

01:03:12.205 --> 01:03:13.498
He doesn't like her.

01:03:13.956 --> 01:03:15.875
You're really out of line.

01:03:15.958 --> 01:03:17.835
How could you hurt him like this?

01:03:17.919 --> 01:03:19.670
I can be a lot worse than this.

01:03:20.630 --> 01:03:23.382
Why don't you know that I'm trying
my best to hold myself back?

01:03:24.050 --> 01:03:25.843
If I could have my way,

01:03:25.927 --> 01:03:28.304
I'd make sure you guys
never set foot in our place again.

01:03:28.387 --> 01:03:29.555
Enough!

01:03:30.848 --> 01:03:31.766
What did you just say?

01:03:34.602 --> 01:03:35.686
I'll break up with him.

01:03:38.356 --> 01:03:39.440
I will.

01:03:41.526 --> 01:03:44.695
I'll end it with him, so please stop.

01:03:46.364 --> 01:03:47.281
Jin-a.

01:03:47.657 --> 01:03:48.991
Enough, all of you.

01:03:56.874 --> 01:03:58.334
Jun-hui.

01:03:59.043 --> 01:04:00.419
Let's talk again another time.

01:04:01.003 --> 01:04:02.672
Let's end it here.

01:04:13.891 --> 01:04:15.059
We should break up.

01:05:12.199 --> 01:05:13.326
Jin-a.

01:05:14.785 --> 01:05:15.786
Jin-a.

01:05:17.079 --> 01:05:18.080
Jin-a.

01:05:19.165 --> 01:05:20.207
Jin-a.

01:05:20.499 --> 01:05:21.876
Jin-a.

01:05:22.877 --> 01:05:24.545
- Jin-a.
- What do you think you're doing now?

01:05:24.629 --> 01:05:26.547
- Jin-a!
- What do you think you're doing?

01:05:26.631 --> 01:05:28.382
- Why are you being like this? Stop it!
- Jin-a.

01:05:28.466 --> 01:05:30.760
- What the hell are you doing?
- Jin-a!

01:05:31.010 --> 01:05:32.678
- Let go.
- Open the door.

01:05:33.930 --> 01:05:35.014
Open up.

01:06:12.426 --> 01:06:14.428
Will you throw your pride away
because you think

01:06:14.512 --> 01:06:17.014
the fact that you two love each other
is all that matters?

01:06:17.098 --> 01:06:18.975
Must you take things this far?

01:06:19.058 --> 01:06:20.434
I'm having a hard time as well.

01:06:20.726 --> 01:06:23.396
It's not like I keep saying I'm okay
because I'm really okay.

01:06:23.521 --> 01:06:25.564
I don't think I need to worry
about Jun-hui anymore.

01:06:25.690 --> 01:06:26.857
He grew up to be a fine man.

01:06:26.941 --> 01:06:29.443
I'm relieved because you chose Jin-a.

01:06:29.944 --> 01:06:31.112
Thank you.

01:06:31.779 --> 01:06:33.364
It might be a lot harder

01:06:33.447 --> 01:06:35.449
- than you are expecting it to be.
- Let go!

01:06:36.200 --> 01:06:38.661
Are you sure
you'll be able to handle the consequences?

01:06:39.912 --> 01:06:41.205
No ramyeon for you if you cry.

01:06:41.872 --> 01:06:43.124
I want ramyeon.

01:06:43.374 --> 01:06:47.044
I've decided to move out
and live on my own.

01:06:48.212 --> 01:06:49.672
Do your parents want you to move out?

01:06:51.007 --> 01:06:52.008
Let's move in together.

01:06:53.718 --> 01:06:55.219
I don't need anything else.

01:06:58.014 --> 01:07:00.266
You're all I need, Jun-hui.

01:07:04.937 --> 01:07:06.939
Subtitle translation by Choi Hyeon-ju
